## ‚ú® Key Features

- **üîß Modular bash configuration** ‚Äî Organized `~/.bashrc.d/` modules with proper shellcheck pragmas
- **üîí GPG-encrypted secrets** ‚Äî Pass integration with automatic migration from plaintext
