- **üì¶ Chezmoi-powered** ‚Äî Declarative dotfiles with dynamic templating
- **‚ö° Atomic operations** ‚Äî Safe file writes with automatic rollback on failure
- **üö´ Secret scanning** ‚Äî Pre-commit hooks with gitleaks + shellcheck
- **‚úÖ CI/CD pipeline** ‚Äî GitHub Actions with proper PR comment permissions
- **üîÑ One-command rollback** ‚Äî Time-stamped backups with restore scripts
- **üìä Health monitoring** ‚Äî Comprehensive doctor script with actionable output
- **üéØ XDG compliance** ‚Äî Full Base Directory specification support
- **üöÄ Version checking** ‚Äî Minimum version requirements for critical tools
- **üåü Fast prompt (optional)** ‚Äî Starship support without heavy frameworks

## üöÄ Quick Start

### Bootstrap (First Time)

